## Data Flow Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[External APIs] --> B[Connector Layer]
    B --> C[Discovery Engine]
    C --> D[Market Data Buffer]
    
    D --> E[Arbitrage Engine]
    E --> F[Opportunity Detector]
    F --> G{Risk Check}
    
    G -->|Low Risk| H[Opportunity Queue]
    G -->|High Risk| I[Discard]
    
    H --> J[Alert Service]
    H --> K[Execution Router]
    
    K --> L{User Tier}
    L -->|Manual| M[Human Review]
    L -->|Simulated| N[Paper Trading]
    L -->|Automated| O[Guardrails Check]
    
    O -->|Pass| P[Trade Execution]
    O -->|Fail| Q[Block + Log]
    
    M --> R{Approve?}
    R -->|Yes| P
    R -->|No| S[Reject]
    
    P --> T[Trade Record]
    T --> U[Audit Log]
    
    J --> U
    Q --> U
    S --> U
```

