## Microservices Interaction

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Discovery
    participant MarketData
    participant ArbitrageEngine
    participant RiskEngine
    participant Execution
    participant Database
    
    Client->>API: Request Opportunities
    API->>Database: Get Cached Opportunities
    Database-->>API: Cached Data
    
    API->>MarketData: Fetch Live Snapshots
    MarketData->>Discovery: Get Active Pairs
    Discovery-->>MarketData: Pair List
    
    MarketData->>External: Fetch Prices
    External-->>MarketData: Price Data
    
    MarketData->>ArbitrageEngine: Detect Opportunities
    ArbitrageEngine->>RiskEngine: Score Risk
    RiskEngine-->>ArbitrageEngine: Risk Scores
    
    ArbitrageEngine->>Database: Store Opportunities
    ArbitrageEngine-->>API: Opportunities List
    
    API-->>Client: JSON Response
    
    loop Every 5 seconds
        Discovery->>External: Update Pair List
        MarketData->>External: Fetch Prices
        ArbitrageEngine->>Database: Store New Opportunities
    end